### Compute Logic

#### [NEW] [engine.py](file:///c:/HelioX/confidence/engine.py)

- `ConfidenceEngine.evaluate_confidence(...)`:
  Takes in all required metrics:
  - `retrieval_coverage` (from Synthesis/Adjudication)
  - [citation_density](file:///c:/HelioX/tests/test_adjudication.py#214-221) (from Adjudication)  
  - `worker_agreement` (from Adjudication consensus)
  - `conflict_severity` (from Adjudication conflict log) — **Note: Inverted** (1.0 - severity) so lower severity yields higher score.
  - [authority_score](file:///c:/HelioX/adjudication/authority.py#39-107) (from Adjudication)
  - `avg_cosine_similarity` (from Retrieval/Adjudication)
  
  **Computes `global_confidence` using `ConfidenceWeights`.**

  Applies decision boundaries:
  - `≥ 0.80` → `DELIVER`
  - `0.60 – 0.79` → `DELIVER_WITH_WARNING`
  - `0.40 – 0.59` → `EXPAND_RETRIEVAL`
  - `< 0.40` → `REQUEST_CLARIFICATION`

